# Mapbox Configuration
# Get your free token from https://account.mapbox.com/
VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.your_mapbox_token_here

# Free Tier Limits:
# - 50,000 map loads per month
# - No credit card required for signup
# - Usage tracking and alerts built into the app

# To set up:
# 1. Visit https://account.mapbox.com/
# 2. Sign up for free account
# 3. Copy your "Default public token" 
# 4. Replace "pk.your_mapbox_token_here" above with your actual token
# 5. Restart your dev server: npm run dev

# Optional: Set up usage alerts in your Mapbox dashboard
# Dashboard → Usage → Alerts → Set alerts at 75% and 90%
